Course structure
-	Morning 	09:00-11:30
-	Lunch break	11:30-12:30
-	Afternoon	12:30-15:00

Regarding hardware
The seminar rooms are equipped with laptops that you can use, however, you are free to use your own devices. We will work with Python and R using a web-server, and therefore you only need a web-browser and your student login credentials in order to complete the course. 

If you would like to use your own laptop, make sure that you have a current version of R and the following packages installed:
•	tidyverse
•	knitr
•	gtsummary
•	flextable
•	readxl

